---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Bookkeeping Cleanup West Hollywood | Projexions"
  description="Projexions specializes in Shopify, Stripe, and bookkeeping cleanup for West Hollywood businesses. Get tax-ready records without the panic."
  currentPath="/"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="homepage-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title serif-heading">Financial Clarity When Records Matter</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Projexions brings order to bookkeeping records—particularly when things have fallen behind, tax filing is approaching, or a CPA can't proceed without cleanup.</p>
        <p class="hero-body">Based in West Hollywood, serving small businesses, agencies, and e-commerce sellers nationwide.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/services" class="btn-primary">View Services</a>
        </div>
        <a href="/estimator" class="estimator-cta">Not sure how far behind you are? Try the Quick Estimator →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Projexions Does -->
  <section class="homepage-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title-large">What Projexions Does</h2>
        <div class="title-underline"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content-wide">
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Projexions helps businesses get their books into a clear, reliable state—and keep them that way. Whether you are facing a multi-year backlog or simply need a steady hand for monthly maintenance, the firm provides structured, project-based support tailored to your specific needs.
        </p>

        <ul class="homepage-list">
          <li><strong>Cleanup & Catch-Up:</strong> Reconciling months or years of neglected bank and credit card activity.</li>
          <li><strong>Monthly Bookkeeping:</strong> Regular reconciliations and categorization to maintain ongoing record integrity.</li>
          <li><strong>Platform Specialization:</strong> Expert reconciliation for Stripe, Shopify, and payment processors where automated data often breaks.</li>
          <li><strong>Expense Organization:</strong> Sorting and categorizing transactions to ensure clear separation between business and personal activity.</li>
          <li><strong>Tax Readiness:</strong> Preparing organized, usable records for seamless handoff to your CPA or tax preparer.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="homepage-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Not Sure Where to Start?</h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">Whether you need cleanup, ongoing support, or just a second opinion—start with a conversation.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-cta-inverse">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .estimator-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--brand-green);
    text-decoration: none;
    background-color: rgba(27, 58, 47, 0.08);
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

</style>
